{
  "stem": "22910.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I suppose the-- being an expert in going bankrupt might also have had something to do with the fact that it was in the 1930s.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I suppose he did try.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was teaching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was buying and selling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, it was-- I was going to public school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a Czech public school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our town had four different school systems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a Czech school because it was Czechoslovakia, and anybody who wanted to go there, went.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it turned out to be mostly the Jews, the Jewish children went there, and a few non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever elected to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had the Hungarian school for the Hungarians, which was the population of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they had another Hungarian school, which was with the Hungarian Catholics, which was really-- you know what Volkdeutsche means?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We call them Schwabs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were originally from Germany, I think, many generations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were still kind of segregated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were Catholics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had a school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And kind of outside town there were Ukrainians, because the whole area was a Ukrainian area, just our town itself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just neighbors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we did have a Jewish neighborhood or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, we lived in a place where our nearest Jewish neighbor was quite far.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So neighbors.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But those were usually the Protestant Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have anything to do with the Catholics, because they lived in different places, and some of them came to the Czech school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in school regularly at 6:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went first, second, and third.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you don't necessarily want to know how brilliant I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't know-- I wasn't brilliant, but I was a good student.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
